                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18311020-197-off1050 t18311020-197-cd1051"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 2s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18311020-197-victim1325" type="victimName">
                        Henry 
